subtests.name: addTransceiver() with sendEncoding.maxFramerate field set to less than 0 should reject with RangeError
addTransceiver('audio') with sendEncoding.maxFramerate should succeed, but remove the maxFramerate, even if it is invalid
setParameters with maxFramerate on an audio sender should succeed, but remove the maxFramerate
setParameters with an invalid maxFramerate on an audio sender should succeed, but remove the maxFramerate
setParameters() with encoding.maxFramerate field set to less than 0 should reject with RangeError
setParameters() with maxFramerate 24->16 should succeed with RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 24->16 should succeed without RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate undefined->16 should succeed with RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate undefined->16 should succeed without RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 24->undefined should succeed with RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 24->undefined should succeed without RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 0->16 should succeed with RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 0->16 should succeed without RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 24->0 should succeed with RTCRtpTransceiverInit
setParameters() with maxFramerate 24->0 should succeed without RTCRtpTransceiverInit
